<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>번개모임</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://ai-public.creatie.ai/gen_page/tailwind-custom.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.5?plugins=forms@0.5.7,typography@0.5.13,aspect-ratio@0.4.2,container-queries@0.1.1"></script>
    <script src="https://ai-public.creatie.ai/gen_page/tailwind-config.min.js" data-color="#000000"
            data-border-radius="small"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">
<jsp:include page="../header.jsp"/>

<main class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden">
        <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">[번개 모임] 강남 맛집 탐방 번개 모임</h1>
                    <div class="mt-2 flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock mr-2"></i>
                        <span>현재 시간: 15:30</span>
                        <span class="mx-2">|</span>
                        <span>마감 시간: 오늘 18:00</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                        모집중
                    </span>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6"><h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">모임
                        정보</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt mt-1 text-custom w-5"></i>
                                <div class="ml-3"><p class="text-gray-900">강남역 2번 출구</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-users mt-1 text-custom w-5"></i>
                                <div class="ml-3"><p class="text-gray-900">참가 인원: 8/10명</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-won-sign mt-1 text-custom w-5"></i>
                                <div class="ml-3"><p class="text-gray-900">참가비: 20,000원</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-clock mt-1 text-custom w-5"></i>
                                <div class="ml-3"><p class="text-gray-900">만나는 시간: 18:00</p></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-6"><h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">번개 설명</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">강남의 숨은 맛집을 함께 탐방하는 즐거운 모임입니다.</p></div>
                        <div class="relative h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mt-6"><img
                                src="https://ai-public.creatie.ai/gen_page/map_placeholder_1280x720.png" alt="지도"
                                class="absolute w-full h-full object-cover"/>
                            <button class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 !rounded-button bg-white text-gray-900 px-4 py-2 shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50">
                                <i class="fas fa-directions mr-2"></i>길찾기
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <button class="w-full !rounded-button bg-custom text-white px-6 py-3 text-lg font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-custom mt-6">
                            참여하기
                        </button>
                    </div>


                </div>

                <div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">참여자 현황</h2>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mx-auto"
                                     src="https://creatie.ai/ai/api/search-image?query=A professional headshot of a young Asian person with a friendly smile, wearing casual attire, against a neutral background&width=100&height=100&orientation=squarish&flag=d6019a56-9de8-4c2d-8d50-91a86b94bcc0&flag=1b028cf0-c964-415c-afa9-2d28c79e1bef&flag=ff746f18-b627-4ac3-8cd1-8f8bd8f0b39b&flag=5e69f760-3546-4b64-ab71-cba6cf757051"
                                     alt="참여자"/>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">민지</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mx-auto"
                                     src="https://creatie.ai/ai/api/search-image?query=A professional headshot of a young Asian person with a confident expression, wearing business casual attire, against a neutral background&width=100&height=100&orientation=squarish&flag=6c43af0d-5b66-4129-b200-fbb08413f8c9&flag=86d80138-3ad4-4add-b909-3bba675e33f5&flag=485440f9-a6ec-4c80-b66b-eb2b56077b1f&flag=c7d1e05d-cd0c-4c0b-a484-e9c4ee00df88"
                                     alt="참여자"/>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">준호</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mx-auto"
                                     src="https://creatie.ai/ai/api/search-image?query=A professional headshot of a middle-aged Asian person with glasses, wearing formal attire, against a neutral background&width=100&height=100&orientation=squarish&flag=62df81cb-9ffd-4dd6-9832-bf5606457d0e&flag=d09ad6cf-2650-401c-91c5-7d469fd66384&flag=9de650d6-912a-4732-aa16-50a709230d74&flag=4b1c28e9-5e7a-413e-9199-f687533d7a55"
                                     alt="참여자"/>
                                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">서연</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">실시간 채팅</h2>
                        <div class="h-64 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 overflow-y-auto">
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="flex items-start">
                                    <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full"
                                         src="https://creatie.ai/ai/api/search-image?query=A professional headshot of a young Asian person with a friendly smile, wearing casual attire, against a neutral background&width=100&height=100&orientation=squarish&flag=b54ab06c-4a5d-4ece-9179-ac2354796aab&flag=2e16f07b-c8bc-452a-ae7f-342c75c044c1&flag=70e53fae-230d-413a-adc7-36a228937cdc&flag=34b113d6-9224-44a3-9d72-76dd19d9e85b"
                                         alt="채팅 프로필"/>
                                    <div class="ml-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-3">
                                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">민지</p>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">다들 몇시에 모이나요?</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start">
                                    <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full"
                                         src="https://creatie.ai/ai/api/search-image?query=A professional headshot of a young Asian person with a confident expression, wearing business casual attire, against a neutral background&width=100&height=100&orientation=squarish&flag=22a18a20-f970-41e0-8791-43e13ed582f7&flag=2c577ab0-7218-431c-be1b-e5bcd1bb2081&flag=054203d6-b430-41c6-a897-b136ca895cdb&flag=f8e480a2-52e5-401b-aaa8-ee886dc06a5e"
                                         alt="채팅 프로필"/>
                                    <div class="ml-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-3">
                                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">준호</p>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">6시에 만나요!</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex">
                            <input type="text"
                                   class="flex-1 rounded-l-lg border-gray-300 focus:ring-custom focus:border-custom"
                                   placeholder="메시지를 입력하세요"/>
                            <button class="!rounded-r-button bg-custom text-white px-4 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-custom">
                                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
